ike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T12:45:54.000Z","msg":"日日都有戴 <br />\n但係搭車、出街都係得嗰一個半個人戴真係有啲恢<br />\n<br />\n成日話和勇不分 同前線手足同行<br />\n大家就做多少少啦好嘛 平日多啲人戴口罩<br />\n前線手足見到起碼都會多種有同行者嘅感覺<br />\n千祈唔好睇少呢樣嘢 越多人戴個感覺就越強烈<br />\n除左係可以幫前線打氣嘅其中一種行動之外<br />\n亦都係幫緊你自己 幫緊全香港人向港共說不<br />\n當然其他行動都需要你嘅參與<br />\n呢樣只不過係日常抗爭嘅之一<br />\n<br />\n前線手足付出咗咁多 <br />\n幾廿蚊一包口罩完全講唔上係啲咩成本<br />\n所以求下大家一齊戴啦好嘛 <br />\n一齊感染身邊嘅嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d68904318e9acb1dd2effd7753fde4fc8648925","tid":1666170,"uid":11601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T12:55:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfe0ef7e58ee421d8e80d81dd97bc4e76a94956d","tid":1666170,"uid":138934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T14:07:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5f1dab841da8d9d85d052c90f6e67a73b339779","tid":1666170,"uid":304344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T14:30:17.000Z","msg":"我有戴呀，每次見其他人都有戴都係一份力量，唔理其他人點，我做左我自己嗰份先"},{"pid":"12cfba300fb1d1cb45d78af1b0848c3c85e3c19a","tid":1666170,"uid":319181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T14:46:24.000Z","msg":"唔止謝sir，連er er er sir都&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1644080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1644080</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"42e8f936d2db0c163ac71d01ebaa4981427002f5","tid":1666170,"uid":978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T14:59:08.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d749dfd89100095c59c62e8a963dce608c939f5","tid":1666170,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T15:01:41.000Z","msg":"我有架 日日戴"},{"pid":"9636642860b6f258fed025ef569db63ddd134df5","tid":1666170,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7e